@startuml delivery-sequence-create-delivery
title Delivery: Create a Delivery Request

actor User
participant "Frontend\n(Angular)" as FE
participant "Backend API\n(Spring Boot)" as API
participant "Pricing Engine" as PRICING
participant "Vehicle Service" as VEHICLE
participant "Assignment Service" as ASSIGN
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> FE: Navigate to "Create Delivery"
FE -> API: GET /api/orders (user's orders)
API -> DB: SELECT orders WHERE userId = ?
DB --> API: Order list
API --> FE: 200 OK (orders)
FE --> User: Display order selection

User -> FE: Select order and\ndelivery address
FE -> API: POST /api/deliveries/initiate\n{orderId, addressId}
API -> DB: SELECT order, address
DB --> API: Order + address data

API -> PRICING: calculate(order, address)
PRICING -> PRICING: compute distance\nweight, dimensions
PRICING --> API: price = 12.50 TND

API -> VEHICLE: findBestVehicle(weight, dimensions, distance)
VEHICLE -> DB: SELECT vehicles\nWHERE capacity >= ? AND available
DB --> VEHICLE: Matching vehicles
VEHICLE --> API: vehicleId = 42 (motorcycle)

API --> FE: 200 OK\n{price: 12.50, vehicle: motorcycle, estimatedTime: 45min}
FE --> User: Display delivery summary\nwith cost and vehicle type

User -> FE: Select payment method\nand confirm
FE -> API: POST /api/deliveries/confirm\n{deliveryRequestId, paymentMethod}
API -> DB: INSERT delivery_request\nSET status = PENDING

API -> ASSIGN: assignCourier(vehicleId, zone)
ASSIGN -> DB: SELECT courier_profiles\nWHERE approved = true AND zone = ?
DB --> ASSIGN: Available couriers
ASSIGN -> DB: UPDATE delivery_request\nSET courierId = ?, status = ASSIGNED
ASSIGN --> API: Courier assigned (courierId = 7)

API --> FE: 201 Created (deliveryReference)
FE --> User: Delivery confirmation\ndisplayed with tracking reference
@enduml
